text: Andrej Martin and Hans Podlipnik Castillo were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Sadio Doumbia and Fabien Reboul won the title after defeating Sergio Galdós and Facundo Mena 6–3, 7–6(7–4) in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Banja Luka Challenger - Doubles 2019 Doubles
